    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Marriage Impossible 2  is a  game playable for a streamer with 45~ viewers.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The goal is to collaborate with viewers and streamers to marry all viewers!❤️ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >*The game supports streaming service like Twitch, YouTube, Chzzk. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >*Photo Mode </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Take a picture with viewers!  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Capture memories in photos that will last a lifetime! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Streamer :  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Mouse and keyboard to use spells. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Chat Viewer : </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Command : &quot;Join&quot; to join game </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >1/2/3 : Spawn a unit to each number's position. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Key Feature : </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-streamer-only game. Twitch, YouTube, Chzzk supports. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-Fast paced realtime strategy. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-Various unique events. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-Photo mode.</p>",
